In order to capture pcd files:

Navigate to your directory of choice and run the command:
rosrun pcl_ros pointcloud_to_pcd input:=/<your_pointcloud_topic>

To publish a pointcloud:

Navigate to the directory containing your pcd files and run the command:
rosrun pcl_ros pcd_to_pointcloud <your_pcd_file>.pcd <period> _frame_id:=/<target_frame>
